✨ JOIN us at the Therapeutic Market✨ 

随着Finals和各种Deadlines的步步紧逼，努力学习的你也别忘了劳逸结合才是效率学习的秘诀！ CSSA准备了一系列超治愈解压活动，手工、冥想、零食自由pick！快来和CSSA一起迎接Finals吧💨

Fried by finals and  deadlines? Come chill, meditate, and snack your stress away with us at our Therapeutic Market. We’ve got lots of fun activities to recharge you before the final stretch ! 🧘‍♀️🎨
